title: NBA Draftapalooza, Part 4: Winners + Losers With Ryen Russillo and Kevin O’Connor
description:
The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Ryen Russillo and Kevin O’Connor to discuss a long list of winners and losers from the first round of the NBA draft.

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Ryen Russillo and Kevin O’Connor
Producer: Kyle Crichton
